=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 400;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;=\"\" float:=\"\" none;\"=\"\">Zu beachten ist das Nds. FischG, die Binnenfischereiordnung und der Rd. Erl. D. ML. vom 01.03.1978.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 400;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 400;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;=\"\" float:=\"\" none;\"=\"\">Gemeinschaftsangeln bedü</span>rfen grundsätzlich vorab der Genehmigung der Besatzgemeinschaft Ems I.<br><b>Zelten und Lagern ist verboten</b>!</li><li>Der Fischereierlaubnisschein ist nur zusammen mit dem Fischereischein gültig!</li><li>Fänge sind auf hejfish.com unter \"Angelkarten &amp; Käufe\" zu melden! Bitte auch Leermeldungen (nichts gefangen) abgeben. Andernfalls wird keine weitere Karte ausgegeben!</li></ul><p>\r\n</p><p>\r\n</p><p>\r\n</p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>1. Besondere Auflagen</b></h4><ul><li>Jugendliche unter 14 Jahren dürfen den Fischfang nur zur Vorbereitung auf die Sportfischerprüfung und unter Aufsicht eines berechtigten volljährigen Anglers ausüben. (In Ruf- und Sichtweite!)\r\n</li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 400;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" left;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;=\"\" float:=\"\" none;\"=\"\">Für<span>&nbsp;</span></span><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" left;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">Hunde<span>&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 400;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" left;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;=\"\" float:=\"\" none;\"=\"\">besteht<span>&nbsp;</span></span><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" left;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">Leinenzwang</b><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 400;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" left;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;=\"\" float:=\"\" none;\"=\"\">!</span></li><li><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" left;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">Das Befahren von Wiesen, Äckern ist verboten.</b><b></b><br>Das Fischen mit <b>eingefärbten Ködern</b> sowie die Verwendung <b>eingefärbter Lockmittel sind untersag</b>t.&nbsp;<br><b>Wasserfahrzeuge sind nicht zugelassen.</b></li></ul>","rules_files":[],"tickets":[{"name":"Tageskarte - Normalpreis inkl. Servicegebühr","price":"13,00 EUR","ticket_type_id":7837,"price_id":102163},{"name":"Tageskarte - Jugendpreis inkl. Servicegebühr (ab 14 Jahre)","price":"8,00 EUR","ticket_type_id":7837,"price_id":102164}],"ticket_types":[{"id":7837,"name":"Tageskarte","category":"DAY","duration":1,"prices":[{"id":102163,"name":"Normalpreis inkl. Servicegebühr","value":"13,00 EUR","cents":1300,"type":"DEFAULT","valid_from":"2026-05-01","valid_to":"2026-10-31","available_from":"2026-04-15","age":0,"eligible":true},{"id":102164,"name":"Jugendpreis inkl. Servicegebühr (ab 14 Jahre)","value":"8,00 EUR","cents":800,"type":"JUNIOR","valid_from":"2026-05-01","valid_to":"2026-10-31","available_from":"2026-04-15","age":17,"eligible":true}],"licenses":{"required":["Fischereischein / Jugendfischereischein Deutschland"],"optional":[]},"rules_text":"<h5 style=\"text-align: center; \"><b>Bestimmungen</b></h5><p><b>1. Fangbeschränkung:<br></b><b>Nur drei Edelfische</b> entnehmen! Hecht, Zander, Karpfen, Schleie, alle Forellenartige. Alle anderen keine Begrenzung.</p><p>\r\n</p><p><b>2. Mindestmaße &amp; Schonzeiten</b></p><p>\r\n\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\n\ttable.tableizer-table {\r\n\t\tfont-size: 8px;\r\n\t\tborder: 1px solid #000; \r\n\t\tfont-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\r\n\t} \r\n\t.tableizer-table td {\r\n\t\tpadding: 1px;\r\n\t\tmargin: 1px;\r\n\t\tborder: 1px solid #000;\r\n\t}\r\n\t.tableizer-table th {\r\n\t\tbackground-color: #00C1D6; \r\n\t\tcolor: #000;\r\n\t\tfont-weight: bold;\r\n\t}\r\n</style>\r\n</p><table class=\"tableizer-table\">\r\n<thead><tr class=\"tableizer-firstrow\"><th>Art </th><th>Mindestmaß</th><th>Schonzeit</th></tr></thead><tbody>\r\n <tr><td>Aal</td><td>45 cm</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;--</td></tr>\r\n <tr><td>Barbe</td><td>50 cm</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;--</td></tr>\r\n <tr><td>Forelle</td><td>32 cm</td><td>15.10. - 30.04.</td></tr>\r\n <tr><td>Edelkrebs</td><td>11 cm</td><td>01.11. - 30.06.</td></tr>\r\n <tr><td>Graskarpfen</td><td>60 cm</td><td> </td></tr>\r\n <tr><td>Hecht</td><td>55 cm</td><td>01.02. - 30.05.</td></tr>\r\n <tr><td>Karpfen</td><td>40 cm</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;--</td></tr>\r\n <tr><td>Quappe</td><td>40 cm</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;--</td></tr>\r\n <tr><td>Rapfen</td><td>40 cm</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;--</td></tr>\r\n <tr><td>Schleie</td><td>30 cm</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;--</td></tr>\r\n <tr><td>Wels</td><td>entfällt</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">Entnahmepflicht</td></tr>\r\n <tr><td>Zander</td><td>50 cm</td><td>01.02. - 30.05</td></tr>\r\n <tr><td>alle anderen</td><td>18 cm</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;--</td></tr>\r\n</tbody></table>\r\n\r\n<p></p><p>Untermaßige Fische müssen schonend zurückgesetzt werden. Sind diese nicht mehr lebensfähig, sind sie sofort unschädlich zu beseitigen, ihre Verwertung ist verboten!&nbsp;</p><p>Alle anderen Fische haben ein Mindestmaß von 18cm. Ausnahme: Weißfische und Gründeln dürfen als Köderfische auch kleiner als 18cm entnommen werden. Es dürfen nur 10 Köderfische gehältert werden.&nbsp;</p><p><b>3. Allgemeine Bestimmungen</b></p><ul><li>Zwei Angelruten für Erwachsene und Jugendliche ab 16 Jahren.\r\n</li><li>Eine Angelrute für Jugendliche ab 10 Jahren\r\n</li><li>Boote dürfen nicht benutzt werden.\r\n</li><li>Futterboote dürfen benutzt werden.\r\n</li><li>Bei Ansitz über 8 STD. muss eine Campingtoilette mitgeführt werden. \r\n</li><li>Es dürfen keine Grundeln als Köderfische benutzt werden. Es dürfen höchstens 10 Köderfische, auch unter 18 cm mitgeführt werden.</li></ul><p><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">4. Gewässerordnung</span><br></p><ul><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 400;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;=\"\" float:=\"\" none;\"=\"\">Jegliches Fischen mit<span>&nbsp;</span></span><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">Köderfischen<span>&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 400;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;=\"\" float:=\"\" none;\"=\"\">und<span>&nbsp;</span></span><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">Kunstködern<span>&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 400;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;=\"\" float:=\"\" none;\"=\"\">ist<span>&nbsp;</span></span><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">vom 01.02. bis 30.05. verboten</b><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 400;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;=\"\" float:=\"\" none;\"=\"\">!</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 400;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;=\"\" float:=\"\" none;\"=\"\">Das Fischen mit eingefärbten Ködern sowie die Verwendung eingefärbter Lockmittel sind untersagt.</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 400;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;=\"\" float:=\"\" none;\"=\"\">Es besteht eine </span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" float:=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><b>Futterbegrenzung </b></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 400;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;=\"\" float:=\"\" none;\"=\"\">von </span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" float:=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><b>einem Liter pro Tag</b></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 400;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;=\"\" float:=\"\" none;\"=\"\">! Es darf ausschließlich während des Angelns gefüttert werden. Vorfüttern ist verboten!</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 400;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;=\"\" float:=\"\" none;\"=\"\">Zu beachten ist das Nds. FischG, die Binnenfischereiordnung und der Rd. Erl. D. ML. vom 01.03.1978.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 400;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 255);=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgb